    DefaultVisualModule6

    public abstract class AbstractVisualModule
extends AbstractPerceptualModule
implements IVisualModule, IParameterized
    abstract impl that address most of the trivial details. Clients must provide and configure the actual IVisualMemory used.
    Author:
    harrison
    See Also:
